## Border Radius

The theme uses a pill-shaped aesthetic for interactive elements and generous rounding on containers.

| Category | Radius | Notes |
|----------|--------|-------|
| Buttons / Inputs | `10rem` / `8.6rem` | Fully pill-shaped |
| Product cards | `2.8rem` (28px) | |
| Collection cards / Modals / Tooltips / Mega menu | `2rem` (20px) | |
| Badges | `1.6rem` (16px) | |
| General large | `2rem` (20px) | |
| General medium | `1.5rem` (15px) | |
| General small / Images | `1rem` (10px) | |
| General XS / Textareas / Add-to-cart | `0.6rem` (6px) | |
| Tags | `0.5rem` (5px) | |
| Circles | `50%` | |
| Article cards / Drawers | `0` | Sharp edges |

## Shadows

All shadows are disabled (opacity: 0). Design is flat ŌĆö use color contrast and spacing for visual depth, not box-shadows.

